data.description: PNGISD AND UPDATED!!! Located in walking distance to Port Neches Primary campus, this home is open concept, with 3bedrooms, 2 full baths, and half of the garage was converted to a room with a window unit and electric, perfect for your mancave!!! (Can easily be converted back to 2 car garage) The sheetrock, plumbing, doors and so much more have been updated!!! New roof and decking in 2022. Located in a family friendly neighborhood with a large, fenced in backyard! Hurry before this beauty is gone!!!
